"""Parse object with no uvs"""
meshes = pywavefront.Wavefront(fixture('simple_normals.obj'))
self.mesh1 = meshes.mesh_list[0]
self.mesh2 = meshes.mesh_list[1]
self.assertEqual(self.mesh1.materials[0].vertices, [20.0, 21.0, 22.0, 0.04,
    0.05, 0.06, 20.0, 21.0, 22.0, 0.01, 0.02, 0.03, 20.0, 21.0, 22.0, 0.07,
    0.08, 0.09])
self.assertEqual(self.mesh2.materials[0].vertices, [0.0, 1.0, -0.0, -1.0, 
    0.0, 1.0, 0.0, 1.0, -0.0, 1.0, 0.0, 1.0, 0.0, 1.0, -0.0, 1.0, 0.0, -1.0])
self.assertEqual(self.mesh2.materials[0].vertex_format, 'N3F_V3F')
